sentence.text: Results We demonstrated an association between six previously published single nucleotide polymorphisms (rs15869 [ BRCA2], rs1805389 [ LIG4], rs8079544 [ TP53], rs25489 [ XRCC1], rs1673041 [ POLD1], and rs11615 [ nucleotide-excision repair]) and subsequent CNS tumors in survivors of childhood cancer.
